message.body: @pjsgamerboy Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input). Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions: N, S, W, E, North, South, West, East, this works for C buttons and D-Pad too. ex: CN, CNorth, DS, DSouth, etc. Up to 3 DIFFERENT commands can be used AT THE SAME TIME, NOT ONE AFTER

fragments.text: @pjsgamerboy Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input). Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions: N, S, W, E, North, South, West, East, this works for C buttons and D-Pad too. ex: CN, CNorth, DS, DSouth, etc. Up to 3 DIFFERENT commands can be used AT THE SAME TIME, NOT ONE AFTER

message.body: ANOTHER: b+up+right. You can't use opposite commands at the same time: Left+Right, Up+Down, etc., WILL NOT WORK. End your input with - to hold down indefinitely until the next input comes: a+z+right-. Alternatively, you can type Wait or Stop to stop the execution of a held input. Sending a normal (Non-held) input if the input is the same as the current held input, it will just hold for a little longer before releasing. Normal (Non-held) inputs last 266 milliseconds, which is around 16 frames on

commenter.bio: I am a bot that likes to do weird things on Twitch along with helping out the Storm Chasers. Do you storm chase on Twitch and want to get me setup on your channel? Contact The Chef#1337 on Discord. Wow Deku OneHand

message.body: @trevdyt Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input). Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions: N, S, W, E, North, South, West, East, this works for C buttons and D-Pad too. ex: CN, CNorth, DS, DSouth, etc. Up to 3 DIFFERENT commands can be used AT THE SAME TIME, NOT ONE AFTER

message.body: ANOTHER: b+up+right. You can't use opposite commands at the same time: Left+Right, Up+Down, etc., WILL NOT WORK. End your input with - to hold down indefinitely until the next input comes: a+z+right-. Alternatively, you can type Wait or Stop to stop the execution of a held input. Sending a normal (Non-held) input if the input is the same as the current held input, it will just hold for a little longer before releasing. Normal (Non-held) inputs last 266 milliseconds, which is around 16 frames on
